name: Air China Cargo 777-FFT [B-2096] Landing and Takeoff at Edmonton Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Back in September 2015, Air China Cargo opened up a new route from Shanghai to Edmonton to Dallas-Fort Worth (and back again) 3 times a week with a Boeing 777 Freighter. I've already caught this bird landing but never got a good shot of the takeoff. Well, without further ado, here is B-2096 landing on runway 30 and taking off 2 hours later with some incredible engine sound. ATC is included on takeoff, enjoy!

Thanks for watching!
